  "detailed_description": "<strong>Stupid Space Shooter</strong> is a top down survivor like where you destroy enemy ships to  gain rewards. Along your way you will face multiple enemies and bosses, and the longer you survive the more Quantum Shards you will receive allowing you to increase your base power.<br><br>SSS brings back the nostalgic feel of arcade games with a modern twist.<br>Use quantum shards to permanently upgrade your ships to allow you to fight to even greater heights.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Multiple weapon types<br></li><li> A skill tree for Meta progression, including but not limited to new weapons, increased base stats, and additional choices<br></li><li> 5 unique enemies, 2 elites that spawn every 15 levels.<br></li><li> Roguelike upgrade choices while you play.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954150/extras/be1a2c3901efb619bd6481c47e283b1c.poster.avif?t=1715915285\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954150/extras/be1a2c3901efb619bd6481c47e283b1c.webm?t=1715915285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954150/extras/be1a2c3901efb619bd6481c47e283b1c.mp4?t=1715915285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Stupid Space Shooter</strong> is a top down survivor like where you destroy enemy ships to  gain rewards. Along your way you will face multiple enemies and bosses, and the longer you survive the more Quantum Shards you will receive allowing you to increase your base power.<br><br>SSS brings back the nostalgic feel of arcade games with a modern twist.<br>Use quantum shards to permanently upgrade your ships to allow you to fight to even greater heights.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Multiple weapon types<br></li><li> A skill tree for Meta progression, including but not limited to new weapons, increased base stats, and additional choices<br></li><li> 5 unique enemies, 2 elites that spawn every 15 levels.<br></li><li> Roguelike upgrade choices while you play.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954150/extras/be1a2c3901efb619bd6481c47e283b1c.poster.avif?t=1715915285\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954150/extras/be1a2c3901efb619bd6481c47e283b1c.webm?t=1715915285\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2954150/extras/be1a2c3901efb619bd6481c47e283b1c.mp4?t=1715915285\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
